Package: qipalette
Title: Quadram Institute Bioscience Color Palettes for Data Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Andrea",
           family = "Telatin",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "andrea.telatin@quadram.ac.uk")
Description: A collection of color palettes for data visualization in R.
    This package provides functions to easily access, display, and use these
    palettes with various plotting systems including base R graphics and ggplot2.
    The palettes are designed to be visually appealing and accessible.
